{"id":"discord-bot-test-suite-c5k.2","title":"Create Go golden contract test suite","description":"Implement black-box contract tests in Go that validate any service implementation.\n\n## Requirements\n- Test Ping (type=1) → Pong (type=1) response\n- Test Slash command (type=2) → deferred response (type=5)\n- Validate Ed25519 signature verification (reject invalid signatures)\n- Verify Pub/Sub message published for slash commands (not for pings)\n- Verify sensitive data redaction (token, signatures, raw body not in logs/messages)\n- Tests run against container image, not internal code\n\n## Test Categories\n1. Signature validation tests\n2. Ping/Pong tests\n3. Slash command tests\n4. Pub/Sub integration tests\n5. Sensitive data redaction tests\n\n## Acceptance Criteria\n- All contract tests pass against reference Go/Gin implementation\n- Tests are reusable for all language implementations\n- Clear test output showing pass/fail status","status":"closed","priority":2,"issue_type":"task","owner":"github@pmgledhill.com","created_at":"2026-01-20T10:51:04.388813Z","created_by":"Paul Gledhill","updated_at":"2026-01-20T14:16:44.998129Z","closed_at":"2026-01-20T14:16:44.998129Z","close_reason":"Closed","dependencies":[{"issue_id":"discord-bot-test-suite-c5k.2","depends_on_id":"discord-bot-test-suite-c5k","type":"parent-child","created_at":"2026-01-20T10:51:04.39096Z","created_by":"Paul Gledhill"}]}
