{"id":"discord-bot-test-suite-c5k.8","title":"Create project directory structure (services/, tests/contract/)","description":"Create project directory structure:\n\n## Directory Layout\n- `services/` - Language/framework implementations\n- `tests/contract/` - Go contract test suite\n\n## Federated .gitignore Strategy\nRoot .gitignore handles shared patterns only (IDE, env, logs, secrets). Each service directory gets its own .gitignore for language-specific artifacts.\n\n### Service Directory Template\nEach service directory should include:\n- `Dockerfile`\n- `.gitignore` (language-specific)\n- Language-appropriate project files (go.mod, requirements.txt, package.json, etc.)\n\n### Per-Service .gitignore Examples\n- Go: `*.test`, `coverage.out`, `/bin/`\n- Python: `__pycache__/`, `.venv/`, `*.pyc`, `.coverage`\n- Node.js: `node_modules/`, `dist/`\n- Java: `target/`, `*.class`, `.gradle/`\n- Rust: `/target/`\n- C#: `bin/`, `obj/`, `*.nupkg`\n- Ruby: `.bundle/`, `log/`, `tmp/`\n- PHP: `/vendor/`\n- C++: `*.o`, `CMakeCache.txt`, `CMakeFiles/`\n\nDefinition of Done:\n- services/ directory exists with placeholder README\n- tests/contract/ directory exists\n- Root .gitignore contains only shared patterns\n- Template .gitignore files documented for each language","status":"closed","priority":2,"issue_type":"task","owner":"github@pmgledhill.com","created_at":"2026-01-20T11:14:02.654945Z","created_by":"Paul Gledhill","updated_at":"2026-01-20T13:39:59.863033Z","closed_at":"2026-01-20T13:39:59.863033Z","close_reason":"Closed","dependencies":[{"issue_id":"discord-bot-test-suite-c5k.8","depends_on_id":"discord-bot-test-suite-c5k","type":"parent-child","created_at":"2026-01-20T11:14:02.657254Z","created_by":"Paul Gledhill"}]}
{"id":"discord-bot-test-suite-c5k.9","title":"Establish quality standards and linting infrastructure","description":"Set up project-wide quality and standards infrastructure:\n\n## Linting\n- Centralized/shared linting config at repo root (editorconfig, prettier, etc.)\n- Language-specific linters in each service folder (golangci-lint, flake8, eslint, etc.)\n- Pre-commit hooks for consistent enforcement\n\n## Dependency Management\n- Dependabot configuration for automated security updates\n- Dependency update policy (frequency, auto-merge rules)\n\n## CI Rules\n- Required status checks for PRs\n- Branch protection rules\n- Test coverage thresholds (if applicable)\n\n## Version Policy\n- Document version selection criteria (modern but stable, not bleeding-edge)\n- Language/framework version matrix\n- Deprecation policy\n\n## Git Standards\n- Commit message format\n- Branch naming conventions\n- PR template\n- CODEOWNERS file\n\nDefinition of Done:\n- All linters configured and passing\n- Dependabot PRs flowing\n- CI enforces quality gates\n- Standards documented in CONTRIBUTING.md or similar","status":"closed","priority":2,"issue_type":"task","owner":"github@pmgledhill.com","created_at":"2026-01-20T13:11:24.594262Z","created_by":"Paul Gledhill","updated_at":"2026-01-20T13:25:13.899304Z","closed_at":"2026-01-20T13:25:13.899304Z","close_reason":"Closed","dependencies":[{"issue_id":"discord-bot-test-suite-c5k.9","depends_on_id":"discord-bot-test-suite-c5k","type":"parent-child","created_at":"2026-01-20T13:11:24.595998Z","created_by":"Paul Gledhill"}]}
